snippet.title: Pathfinder: Wrath of the Righteous - Combat Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn more at https://wrath.owlcatgames.com/
Lead the Crusade against the demonic invasion and rise as a new hero wielding unimaginable powers in a brand new CRPG from creators of Pathfinder: Kingmaker.

Follow our official media to stay up-to-date with any and all news:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/owlcatgames
Discord: https://discord.gg/syqGPZH

Community Quest Trailer: https://youtu.be/YKc2tKiqiNg
Community Quest hub: https://wrath.owlcatgames.com/vote/
